_sText:
Mapper notes: This map has been unfinished for past 2 years I stopped playing CS:S due to "smart" update. I made time and finished it, and it's final version for me. I'm not planning to modify the map further. The file is big because of songs in it. Due to big delay I can't really give v1 to v2 changelog. That you see, it's dark. And really dark. And it's on purpose.

And again due to delay, I don't remember anyone to give credits. So if you are unsatisfied because I forgot you, write me and I will add you to credits. 

If you want, I'll give out the .vmf, under two conditions. 1) write me that you want .vmf 2) if you don't have at least one released map, don't bother yourself with step one ;)

Have fun!
